			p.font-weight-bold.leadership-para Majority Representation
			p We have #{numSeats} seats in the House of Representatives and #{numMps} MPs in the House of Commons.
			img(src="#{graphImg}" alt="graph of representation").img-rounded.img-fluid.float-right
